# Windows Development

This project is developed on **Windows 11** (Intel Core Ultra 5 125H, 15.6 GB RAM, often ~4 GB free).

## Agent Must Do

- Prefer **cross-platform** commands (`npm run`, Node APIs) over macOS-only tools (`pbcopy`, `open`, `sed -i ''`).
- Use **PowerShell-compatible** or Node.js scripts in hooks and tooling.
- Keep **LF line endings** — never commit CRLF-only churn (see `.gitattributes`).
- Be **memory-conscious**: avoid parallel heavy processes (multiple dev servers, full test + build simultaneously).
- Use **forward slashes** in code paths; Windows accepts them in Node/JS tooling.
- Remember Windows filesystem is **case-insensitive** — match import casing exactly.

